txt.en: You have been recognized as a servant to the masters of Shrak Mauruk!
Service to the masters of the Shrak Mauruk will result in the ability to find your way through the city with less effort.
Complete quests for the benefit of Shrak Mauruk!
Shíktarb awaits your return to Shrak Mauruk where he will see you rewarded for your service!
You have performed many services for the masters of the Shrak Mauruk.
